{"video_id": "Gt9GLkuxAWc", "title": "Daily Evening Bhagavatam Discourse | HH Stoka Krishna Swami | SB 1.6.6-10 | 25-10-2021", "speaker": "HH Stoka Krishna Swami", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gt9GLkuxAWc", "duration": 939, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 30.0, "text": " ओम अज्ञानति मिरान्धस्य ज्ञानान्जनिषलाकया चक्षरुन्मीलितं येनातस्मै श्री गुरवेनमहा नमा ओम विष्णु पादाया कृष्ण प्रेष्ठाय भूतले श्रीमते भक्ति वेदान्त स्वामिन्नति नामिने नमस्ते सारस्वते देवे गवरभाणी प्रच"}, {"start": 30.0, "end": 60.0, "text": " प्रभूनित्यानन्द श्री अद्वैत गदाधर श्रीवास अधी गवरभक्त वृन्दा हरे कृष्ण हरे कृष्ण कृष्ण कृष्ण हरे हरे हरे राम हरे रामा राम रामा हरे हरे ओम नमो भगवते वासु देवाया नारायनम नमस्कृत्य नरम चैवन अरोत्तमं देवी"}, {"start": 60.0, "end": 74.8, "text": " This session will be discussing from the Srimad Bhagavatam, the first canto, sixth chapter. Sixth chapter is entitled Conversation between Narada and Vyasa Deva. This is the sixth verse I am going to read now."}, {"start": 74.8, "end": 104.78, "text": " The meaning of this verse is I was the only son of my mother who was not only a simple woman but a maid servant as well."}, {"start": 105.34, "end": 129.9, "text": " Since I was her only offspring, she had no other alternative for protection. She bound me with the tie of affection. This is Narada Muni describing his previous life to Vyasa Deva. He is particularly answering Vyasa's question as to what did he do after initiation."}, {"start": 131.24, "end": 134.78, "text": " So he was the only son of my mother."}, {"start": 134.8, "end": 158.60000000000002, "text": " He was the only son of his mother and his mother was a maid servant doing some simple work and he was her only son. So she bound him up with her affectionate bondage."}, {"start": 161.24, "end": 163.08, "text": " The next verse, the seventh verse."}, {"start": 164.8, "end": 189.64000000000001, "text": " The meaning is she wanted to look after my maintenance properly but because she was not independent, she was not able to do anything for me."}, {"start": 189.64000000000001, "end": 202.32000000000002, "text": " The world is under the full control of the Supreme Lord. Therefore, everyone is like a wooden doll in the hands of a puppet master."}, {"start": 202.32000000000002, "end": 219.32000000000002, "text": " So Narada Muni is explaining that the mother was having a plan to look after this boy very nicely."}, {"start": 219.64000000000001, "end": 230.52, "text": " But we should always remember, none of us in this world are independent."}, {"start": 233.32000000000002, "end": 239.42000000000002, "text": " The world is under the full control, complete control of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 243.08, "end": 245.16000000000003, "text": " It is described here."}, {"start": 246.66000000000003, "end": 249.62, "text": " Therefore, everyone is like a wooden doll in the hands of a puppet master."}, {"start": 249.64000000000001, "end": 250.54000000000002, "text": " It is described here."}, {"start": 250.54000000000002, "end": 251.70000000000002, "text": " Therefore, everyone is like a wooden doll in the hands of a puppet master."}, {"start": 251.70000000000002, "end": 252.64000000000001, "text": " It is described here."}, {"start": 253.60000000000002, "end": 258.5, "text": " So does it mean that what can we do?"}, {"start": 258.92, "end": 263.76, "text": " Whatever happens is completely under the control of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 263.96000000000004, "end": 269.06, "text": " So we are kind of totally helpless."}, {"start": 270.90000000000003, "end": 277.06, "text": " This sort of understanding is not the correct understanding."}, {"start": 277.06, "end": 286.06, "text": " What is the correct understanding? The Lord is in full control, yes, that's a fact."}, {"start": 286.06, "end": 299.06, "text": " But he also has given each of the human beings, particularly, a little free will, little independence."}, {"start": 299.06, "end": 310.06, "text": " And we have to become responsible in properly utilizing the tiny amount of independence."}, {"start": 310.06, "end": 324.06, "text": " Now this use of independence is dependent on our desires."}, {"start": 324.06, "end": 328.06, "text": " In what way we want to cultivate our desires."}, {"start": 328.06, "end": 329.06, "text": " In what way we want to cultivate our desires."}, {"start": 329.06, "end": 336.06, "text": " So, depending on the desires and depending on our past karma,"}, {"start": 336.06, "end": 342.06, "text": " So, depending on the desires and depending on our past karma,"}, {"start": 342.06, "end": 353.06, "text": " the Supreme Lord arranges everything for a person, for each one of us."}, {"start": 353.06, "end": 358.06, "text": " So, ultimately, the Supreme Lord is in control."}, {"start": 358.06, "end": 371.06, "text": " Our specific enjoyment and suffering is due to our own actions, our desires."}, {"start": 371.06, "end": 376.06, "text": " It is not imposed by the Lord."}, {"start": 376.06, "end": 379.06, "text": " Desires are not imposed."}, {"start": 379.06, "end": 382.06, "text": " Activities are not imposed."}, {"start": 382.06, "end": 385.06, "text": " So, therefore, we have to carefully understand that,"}, {"start": 385.06, "end": 387.06, "text": " So, therefore, we have to carefully understand that,"}, {"start": 387.06, "end": 389.06, "text": " So, therefore, we have to carefully understand the statement here,"}, {"start": 389.06, "end": 390.06, "text": " So, therefore, we have to carefully understand the statement here,"}, {"start": 390.06, "end": 394.06, "text": " that we are not independent,"}, {"start": 394.06, "end": 396.06, "text": " that whatever we want, we can do."}, {"start": 396.06, "end": 398.06, "text": " No."}, {"start": 398.06, "end": 403.06, "text": " There is always a control."}, {"start": 403.06, "end": 406.06, "text": " The supreme control."}, {"start": 406.06, "end": 411.06, "text": " Not just a control, but the supreme control of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 411.06, "end": 416.06, "text": " That we are bound up based on our past actions,"}, {"start": 416.06, "end": 420.06, "text": " and based on our desires,"}, {"start": 420.06, "end": 431.06, "text": " to have a certain freedom within a boundary."}, {"start": 431.06, "end": 434.06, "text": " We are not having any absolute freedom."}, {"start": 434.06, "end": 442.06, "text": " Absolute freedom belongs only to the Supreme Lord and nobody else."}, {"start": 442.06, "end": 444.06, "text": " So, I continue."}, {"start": 444.06, "end": 446.06, "text": " The eighth verse."}, {"start": 466.06, "end": 468.06, "text": " The meaning of this verse is,"}, {"start": 468.06, "end": 471.06, "text": " When I was a mere child of five years,"}, {"start": 471.06, "end": 473.06, "text": " I lived in a Brahmana school."}, {"start": 473.06, "end": 476.06, "text": " I was dependent on my mother's affection,"}, {"start": 476.06, "end": 480.06, "text": " and had no experience of different lands."}, {"start": 480.06, "end": 486.06, "text": " Very limited scope for the boy to do anything."}, {"start": 486.06, "end": 490.06, "text": " He was just a five-year-old boy."}, {"start": 490.06, "end": 494.06, "text": " And he was living in a Brahmana school."}, {"start": 494.06, "end": 497.06, "text": " And he was dependent on his mother."}, {"start": 497.06, "end": 502.06, "text": " The next verse, further Narad Muni explains, describes,"}, {"start": 503.06, "end": 504.06, "text": " Ninth verse,"}, {"start": 504.06, "end": 508.06, "text": " Ekadā nirgatāṁ yehād,"}, {"start": 508.06, "end": 512.06, "text": " Duhantīṁ nishigāṁ patī,"}, {"start": 512.06, "end": 516.06, "text": " Sarpo adasat padās prishtah,"}, {"start": 516.06, "end": 520.06, "text": " Kripanāṁ kāla choditah."}, {"start": 520.06, "end": 521.06, "text": " The meaning is,"}, {"start": 521.06, "end": 523.06, "text": " Once upon a time,"}, {"start": 523.06, "end": 524.06, "text": " my poor mother,"}, {"start": 524.06, "end": 527.06, "text": " when going out one night to milk a cow,"}, {"start": 527.06, "end": 529.06, "text": " was bitten on the leg by a serpent,"}, {"start": 529.06, "end": 532.06, "text": " influenced by supreme time."}, {"start": 533.0600000000001, "end": 542.0600000000001, "text": " So, this is the supreme will of the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 542.0600000000001, "end": 545.0600000000001, "text": " So, Śrīla Prabhupāda explains,"}, {"start": 545.0600000000001, "end": 551.0600000000001, "text": " That is the way of dragging a sincere soul nearer to God."}, {"start": 551.0600000000001, "end": 556.0600000000001, "text": " The boy was bound up by his mother's affection."}, {"start": 556.0600000000001, "end": 561.0600000000001, "text": " But, to release him from that bondage,"}, {"start": 561.0600000000001, "end": 565.0600000000001, "text": " the Lord has arranged something."}, {"start": 565.0600000000001, "end": 567.0600000000001, "text": " What is that?"}, {"start": 567.0600000000001, "end": 572.0600000000001, "text": " The poor boy was being looked after only by his affectionate mother."}, {"start": 572.0600000000001, "end": 577.0600000000001, "text": " And yet, the mother was taken away from the world by the supreme will,"}, {"start": 577.0600000000001, "end": 584.0600000000001, "text": " in order to put him completely at the mercy of the Lord."}, {"start": 584.0600000000001, "end": 590.0600000000001, "text": " See, this is described here as the Lord's mercy."}, {"start": 590.0600000000001, "end": 593.0600000000001, "text": " Upon this soul,"}, {"start": 593.0600000000001, "end": 594.0600000000001, "text": " Narada,"}, {"start": 594.0600000000001, "end": 601.0600000000001, "text": " in his previous life,"}, {"start": 601.0600000000001, "end": 611.0600000000001, "text": " Actually, each one of us is completely dependent entirely on the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 611.0600000000001, "end": 614.0600000000001, "text": " It is not just the case with this boy, Narada."}, {"start": 614.0600000000001, "end": 617.0600000000001, "text": " It is the case with everyone."}, {"start": 617.0600000000001, "end": 619.0600000000001, "text": " But, we have created,"}, {"start": 619.0600000000001, "end": 624.0600000000001, "text": " artificial sources of dependence,"}, {"start": 624.0600000000001, "end": 628.0600000000001, "text": " based on some bodily connections."}, {"start": 628.0600000000001, "end": 635.0600000000001, "text": " But, all these are simply the effect of the illusory energy."}, {"start": 635.0600000000001, "end": 643.0600000000001, "text": " The body itself is the arrangement of the illusory energy."}, {"start": 643.0600000000001, "end": 647.0600000000001, "text": " So, what to speak of the bodily connections?"}, {"start": 647.0600000000001, "end": 649.0600000000001, "text": " They are all completely governed,"}, {"start": 649.0600000000001, "end": 653.0600000000001, "text": " by kala karma guna."}, {"start": 653.0600000000001, "end": 656.0600000000001, "text": " So, there is no certainty,"}, {"start": 656.0600000000001, "end": 661.0600000000001, "text": " how long a certain relationship will exist,"}, {"start": 661.0600000000001, "end": 668.0600000000001, "text": " and what will be the outcome of a certain relationship,"}, {"start": 668.0600000000001, "end": 670.0600000000001, "text": " at a certain time."}, {"start": 670.0600000000001, "end": 675.0600000000001, "text": " Nobody can actually,"}, {"start": 675.0600000000001, "end": 677.0600000000001, "text": " predict,"}, {"start": 677.0600000000001, "end": 680.0600000000001, "text": " or make a definite plan,"}, {"start": 680.0600000000001, "end": 682.0600000000001, "text": " though we try to,"}, {"start": 682.0600000000001, "end": 684.0600000000001, "text": " make so many plans."}, {"start": 684.0600000000001, "end": 687.0600000000001, "text": " But, all such plans are ultimately,"}, {"start": 687.0600000000001, "end": 689.0600000000001, "text": " nullified,"}, {"start": 689.0600000000001, "end": 696.0600000000001, "text": " by the action of the supreme time."}, {"start": 696.0600000000001, "end": 697.0600000000001, "text": " So, the boy,"}, {"start": 697.0600000000001, "end": 699.0600000000001, "text": " was having only,"}, {"start": 699.0600000000001, "end": 701.0600000000001, "text": " his mother."}, {"start": 701.0600000000001, "end": 703.0600000000001, "text": " And, the mother was taken away,"}, {"start": 703.0600000000001, "end": 706.0600000000001, "text": " so that he could completely come to depend upon,"}, {"start": 706.0600000000001, "end": 708.0600000000001, "text": " the supreme lord."}, {"start": 708.0600000000001, "end": 711.0600000000001, "text": " Who is the only available shelter,"}, {"start": 711.0600000000001, "end": 712.0600000000001, "text": " ultimately,"}, {"start": 712.0600000000001, "end": 714.0600000000001, "text": " and nobody else,"}, {"start": 714.0600000000001, "end": 718.0600000000001, "text": " is the shelter."}, {"start": 718.0600000000001, "end": 720.0600000000001, "text": " The tenth verse,"}, {"start": 720.0600000000001, "end": 727.0600000000001, "text": " tadātadaham īśasya bhaktānāṁśaṁ abhīpsatah"}, {"start": 727.0600000000001, "end": 735.0600000000001, "text": " anugrahaṁ manyamāṇaḥ prātiṣṭham diśaṁ uttarāṁ"}, {"start": 735.0600000000001, "end": 737.0600000000001, "text": " The meaning is,"}, {"start": 737.0600000000001, "end": 740.0600000000001, "text": " I took this as the special mercy of the lord,"}, {"start": 740.0600000000001, "end": 742.0600000000001, "text": " who always desires,"}, {"start": 742.0600000000001, "end": 744.0600000000001, "text": " benediction for his devotees."}, {"start": 744.0600000000001, "end": 745.0600000000001, "text": " And so thinking,"}, {"start": 745.0600000000001, "end": 747.0600000000001, "text": " I started for the north."}, {"start": 751.0600000000001, "end": 753.0600000000001, "text": " So, Śrīla Prabhupāda explains,"}, {"start": 753.0600000000001, "end": 755.0600000000001, "text": " Confidential devotees of the lord,"}, {"start": 755.0600000000001, "end": 756.0600000000001, "text": " see in every step,"}, {"start": 756.0600000000001, "end": 759.0600000000001, "text": " a benedictory direction of the lord."}, {"start": 759.0600000000001, "end": 762.0600000000001, "text": " What is considered to be an odd or difficult moment,"}, {"start": 762.0600000000001, "end": 764.0600000000001, "text": " in the mundane sense,"}, {"start": 764.0600000000001, "end": 767.0600000000001, "text": " accepted as a special mercy of the lord."}, {"start": 767.0600000000001, "end": 772.0600000000001, "text": " This is the position of a devotee."}, {"start": 772.0600000000001, "end": 775.0600000000001, "text": " This boy was initiated,"}, {"start": 775.0600000000001, "end": 777.0600000000001, "text": " instructed,"}, {"start": 777.0600000000001, "end": 781.0600000000001, "text": " and enlightened by the sages,"}, {"start": 781.0600000000001, "end": 783.0600000000001, "text": " even when he was a very small boy."}, {"start": 783.0600000000001, "end": 785.0600000000001, "text": " But he could understand,"}, {"start": 785.0600000000001, "end": 788.0600000000001, "text": " Oh, now that my mother is"}, {"start": 788.0600000000001, "end": 791.0600000000001, "text": " taken away from me,"}, {"start": 791.0600000000001, "end": 793.0600000000001, "text": " who is there for me,"}, {"start": 793.0600000000001, "end": 794.0600000000001, "text": " other than the supreme lord,"}, {"start": 794.0600000000001, "end": 796.0600000000001, "text": " nobody else."}, {"start": 796.0600000000001, "end": 799.0600000000001, "text": " And therefore,"}, {"start": 799.0600000000001, "end": 802.0600000000001, "text": " this boy thought that,"}, {"start": 802.0600000000001, "end": 804.0600000000001, "text": " it's the lord's mercy,"}, {"start": 804.0600000000001, "end": 808.0600000000001, "text": " that I have been placed in a situation,"}, {"start": 808.0600000000001, "end": 811.0600000000001, "text": " where I exclusively have to depend on him."}, {"start": 811.0600000000001, "end": 813.0600000000001, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 813.0600000000001, "end": 816.0600000000001, "text": " he understood that,"}, {"start": 816.0600000000001, "end": 820.0600000000001, "text": " the lord has freed him from this bondage."}, {"start": 823.0600000000001, "end": 824.0600000000001, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 824.0600000000001, "end": 826.0600000000001, "text": " as he was directed,"}, {"start": 826.0600000000001, "end": 829.0600000000001, "text": " or instructed by the sages,"}, {"start": 829.0600000000001, "end": 833.0600000000001, "text": " he actually,"}, {"start": 833.0600000000001, "end": 838.0600000000001, "text": " started towards the north."}, {"start": 838.0600000000001, "end": 840.0600000000001, "text": " North means,"}, {"start": 840.0600000000001, "end": 843.0600000000001, "text": " going to the Himalayas,"}, {"start": 843.0600000000001, "end": 845.0600000000001, "text": " for,"}, {"start": 845.0600000000001, "end": 848.0600000000001, "text": " exclusively,"}, {"start": 848.0600000000001, "end": 850.0600000000001, "text": " meditating upon the supreme lord,"}, {"start": 850.0600000000001, "end": 852.0600000000001, "text": " as directed by,"}, {"start": 853.0600000000001, "end": 857.0600000000001, "text": " the saintly persons."}, {"start": 857.0600000000001, "end": 858.0600000000001, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 858.0600000000001, "end": 861.0600000000001, "text": " it is explained here,"}, {"start": 861.0600000000001, "end": 863.0600000000001, "text": " mundane prosperity is a kind of,"}, {"start": 863.0600000000001, "end": 865.0600000000001, "text": " material fever."}, {"start": 865.0600000000001, "end": 866.0600000000001, "text": " And by the grace of the lord,"}, {"start": 866.0600000000001, "end": 868.0600000000001, "text": " the temperature of this material fever,"}, {"start": 868.0600000000001, "end": 870.0600000000001, "text": " is gradually diminished."}, {"start": 870.0600000000001, "end": 873.0600000000001, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 873.0600000000001, "end": 874.0600000000001, "text": " what,"}, {"start": 874.0600000000001, "end": 878.0600000000001, "text": " we calculate according to our,"}, {"start": 878.0600000000001, "end": 880.0600000000001, "text": " material calculation,"}, {"start": 880.0600000000001, "end": 882.0600000000001, "text": " that is not,"}, {"start": 882.0600000000001, "end": 884.0600000000001, "text": " the proper understanding,"}, {"start": 884.0600000000001, "end": 887.0600000000001, "text": " from the spiritual perspective."}, {"start": 887.0600000000001, "end": 890.0600000000001, "text": " Just like fever,"}, {"start": 890.0600000000001, "end": 894.0600000000001, "text": " is to be reduced."}, {"start": 894.0600000000001, "end": 897.0600000000001, "text": " It's a symptom of an unhealthy body."}, {"start": 897.0600000000001, "end": 898.0600000000001, "text": " Similarly,"}, {"start": 898.0600000000001, "end": 900.0600000000001, "text": " material prosperity,"}, {"start": 900.0600000000001, "end": 903.0600000000001, "text": " which may make us attached materially,"}, {"start": 903.0600000000001, "end": 905.0600000000001, "text": " or bound materially,"}, {"start": 905.0600000000001, "end": 907.0600000000001, "text": " is like a fever,"}, {"start": 907.0600000000001, "end": 909.0600000000001, "text": " unhealthy condition."}, {"start": 909.0600000000001, "end": 911.0600000000001, "text": " So, when it comes down,"}, {"start": 911.0600000000001, "end": 912.0600000000001, "text": " then,"}, {"start": 912.0600000000001, "end": 913.0600000000001, "text": " that,"}, {"start": 913.0600000000001, "end": 915.0600000000001, "text": " we come out of the bondage,"}, {"start": 915.0600000000001, "end": 916.0600000000001, "text": " material bondage."}, {"start": 916.0600000000001, "end": 919.0600000000001, "text": " And that's what happened to Narada Muni."}, {"start": 919.0600000000001, "end": 920.0600000000001, "text": " Of course,"}, {"start": 920.0600000000001, "end": 922.0600000000001, "text": " people do not understand this."}, {"start": 922.0600000000001, "end": 924.0600000000001, "text": " Ordinary people do not understand this."}, {"start": 924.0600000000001, "end": 926.0600000000001, "text": " It's only spiritual,"}, {"start": 926.0600000000001, "end": 928.0600000000001, "text": " perspective,"}, {"start": 928.0600000000001, "end": 932.0600000000001, "text": " which helps us understand this situation."}, {"start": 932.0600000000001, "end": 933.0600000000001, "text": " So, I'll stop here."}, {"start": 933.0600000000001, "end": 934.0600000000001, "text": " Thank you very much."}, {"start": 934.0600000000001, "end": 935.0600000000001, "text": " Hare Krishna."}]}